Package: OHG
Title: Ordered Hypergeometric (Minimum-Hypergeometric) Enrichment
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Mahmoud", "Eladawi", email = "eladawimahmoud@tutamail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Ordered / minimum-hypergeometric (mHG) enrichment test for one ranked
    gene list against a collection of gene sets. Reports significance (a
    permutation-calibrated p-value), localization (cutoff rank and leading-edge
    fraction), and magnitude (a normalized leading-edge score) as three separate,
    never-pre-mixed axes.
